---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import IndexHeroImage from "../../assets/99xof/hero-99xof.png";
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import BaseHead from "../../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import FormattedDate from "../../components/FormattedDate.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from "../../consts";
import SectionLink from "../../components/SectionLink.astro";
import IndexContent from "./index_content.mdx";

const posts = (await getCollection("shorts")).sort(
	(a, b) => b.data.pubDate.valueOf() - a.data.pubDate.valueOf(),
);
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 960px;
			}
			.hero-image {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 100vw;
			}
			.hero-image img {
				display: block;
				margin: 0 auto;
				border-radius: 0px;
				width: 100%;
				height: auto;
				max-height: 300px;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.hero-image img {
					max-height: 160px;
				}
			}
			ul {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 1rem;
				list-style-type: none;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
			}
			ul li {
				width: calc(50% - 1rem);
			}
			ul li * {
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: 0.2s ease;
			}

			ul li img {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
			}
			ul li a {
				display: block;
			}
			.title {
				margin: 0;
				color: rgb(var(--black));
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				line-height: 1;
			}
			.date {
				margin: 0;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
				font-size: 0.8rem;
			}
			ul li a:hover h4,
			ul li a:hover .date {
				color: rgb(var(--accent));
			}

			@media (max-width: 750px) {
				ul {
					gap: 0.5em;
				}
				ul li {
					width: 100%;
					text-align: left;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<div class="hero-image">
			{
				IndexHeroImage && (
					<Image
						layout="full-width"
						src={IndexHeroImage}
						alt="hero image"
						loading="eager"
					/>
				)
			}
		</div>
		<main class="xof">
			<h1 class="">99<i><span class="cursive">x of </span></i></h1>

			<div class="ml-3 lg:ml-12 text-neutral-500 py-12 italic lg:w-1/2">
				<blockquote cite="https://x.com/i/broadcasts/1dRKZazegnAxB">
					<p>
						…if you could only develop one habit so you could be more successful
						and happy, what would it be?
					</p>
				</blockquote>
				<p>—Brian Tracey, <cite>X Live Broadcast</cite></p>
			</div>

			<h2>What is 99<i><span class="cursive">x of </span></i>?</h2>

			<p>
				It is a work in progress. 99<i><span class="cursive">x of </span></i> is
				my shorthand for the belief that we can fundamentally change/add personal
				traits to increase our happiness and reduce self-induced pains and frustrations.
			</p>

			<p>I am working on two parts.</p>

			<h2>1. Theory</h2>
			<p>
				The first will be a series about my learnings, notes, and previous
				experiences and personal experiments with creating personal lasting
				change.
			</p>

			<section class="hidden">
				<h2>Chapters</h2>
				<SectionLink label="Introduction" url="" status="not started" />
				<SectionLink
					label="If you could change on thing..."
					url=""
					status="not started"
				/>
				<SectionLink
					label="Habits & Foundational Change"
					url="/"
					status="draft"
				/>
				<SectionLink label="Better grab a pen" url="" status="not started" />
				<SectionLink label="Awareness" url="" status="not started" />
				<SectionLink label="Habit Tracking" url="" status="not started" />
				<SectionLink
					label="Setting Intent & Calling Your Shot"
					url=""
					status="not started"
				/>
				<SectionLink label="Evaluation" url="" status="not started" />
				<SectionLink label="Impulse and Action" url="" status="not started" />
				<SectionLink
					label="Getting to know yourself"
					url=""
					status="not started"
				/>
				<SectionLink label="99 to 100 || 99 to 0" url="" status="not started" />
			</section>

			<section>
				<article>
					<h2>2. Personal Experiments</h2>
					<div id="personal-experiments">
						<p>
							The second will be ongoing experiments including this first one on
							"building grit" -- my answer to Brian Tracey's question.
						</p>

						<p>
							My life so far has been full of theory and far too little action.
							Theory without action can deceive me into thinking that I know more than I really do. I am looking to put myself under public scrutiny as I attempt to apply
							everything I think know about change into a series of experiments, both personal and willing volunteers.
						</p>
						<SectionLink
							label="Building Grit 2025"
							url=""
							status="in progress"
						/>
					</div>
				</article>
			</section>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
